That\'s right - Warframe is free! Which means our drop system is designed to maintain a balance. Our free players can earn the game\'s content, and our paying players who support us with purchases usually get first dibs on the content by using Platinum (which can be traded to free players)!    This is automatically generated from our internal data but this data comes with no guarantees -- do not expect it to be comprehensive for how complex the game is.   This list will be maintained by an automated process combined with manual publishing with Updates (not all Hotfixes). We update often and new game systems may or may not be covered here.
